---
description: Form system rules — react-hook-form, zod, shared field components, DataTable.
globs: src/components/form/**,src/features/**/form*,src/features/**/Form*,**/*.schema.ts,**/*.form.tsx
alwaysApply: false
---

Read `.claude/rules/forms.md` for the full form rules.

Key points: use `<Form>` wrapper + components from `src/components/form/`. Use `formValidator` helpers for zod validation. Never raw `<input>/<select>/<textarea>`. For lists, use `<DataTable>`.
